panels.html_data:
This grafana server is a data output of all dry runs (and some live). We are looking for dry running more strategies in different versions and see which variables are the best for those. We intend to introduce backtests on a different dashboard too and cut down the strategies to 7 days in the foreseeable future.

If you want to join our discord of crypto trading enthusiasts you are most welcome. https://discord.gg/yzU6SQpDxN
News and changes are announced at the discord including how you should interprete the shown data.

SELECT
sell_reason AS "Sell Reason",
(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM trades WHERE close_profit > 0 AND c2.sell_reason = sell_reason) AS Wins,
(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM trades WHERE close_profit < 0 AND c2.sell_reason = sell_reason) AS Losses,
(SELECT AVG(close_profit * 100) FROM trades WHERE c2.sell_reason = sell_reason) AS "Avg",
(SELECT SUM(close_profit_abs) FROM trades WHERE c2.sell_reason = sell_reason) AS "Profit"
FROM trades c2 WHERE sell_reason IS NOT NULL GROUP BY sell_reason
